39MultiFormatWriter::encode(const std::wstring& contents, int width, int height) const
40{
41 auto exec0 = [&](auto&& writer) {
42 if (_margin >=0)
43 writer.setMargin(_margin);
44 return writer.encode(contents, width, height);
45 };
46
47 auto AztecEccLevel = [&](Aztec::Writer& writer, int eccLevel) { writer.setEccPercent(eccLevel * 100 / 8); };
48 auto Pdf417EccLevel = [&](Pdf417::Writer& writer, int eccLevel) { writer.setErrorCorrectionLevel(eccLevel); };
49 auto QRCodeEccLevel = [&](QRCode::Writer& writer, int eccLevel) {
50 writer.setErrorCorrectionLevel(static_cast<QRCode::ErrorCorrectionLevel>(--eccLevel / 2));
51 };
52
53 auto exec1 = [&](auto&& writer, auto setEccLevel) {
54 if (_encoding != CharacterSet::Unknown)
55 writer.setEncoding(_encoding);
56 if (_eccLevel >= 0 && _eccLevel <= 8)
57 setEccLevel(writer, _eccLevel);
58 return exec0(std::move(writer));
59 };
60
61 switch (_format) {
62 case BarcodeFormat::AZTEC: return exec1(Aztec::Writer(), AztecEccLevel);
63 case BarcodeFormat::DATA_MATRIX: return exec0(DataMatrix::Writer());
64 case BarcodeFormat::PDF_417: return exec1(Pdf417::Writer(), Pdf417EccLevel);
65 case BarcodeFormat::QR_CODE: return exec1(QRCode::Writer(), QRCodeEccLevel);
66 case BarcodeFormat::CODABAR: return exec0(OneD::CodabarWriter());
67 case BarcodeFormat::CODE_39: return exec0(OneD::Code39Writer());
68 case BarcodeFormat::CODE_93: return exec0(OneD::Code93Writer());
69 case BarcodeFormat::CODE_128: return exec0(OneD::Code128Writer());
70 case BarcodeFormat::EAN_8: return exec0(OneD::EAN8Writer());
71 case BarcodeFormat::EAN_13: return exec0(OneD::EAN13Writer());
72 case BarcodeFormat::ITF: return exec0(OneD::ITFWriter());
73 case BarcodeFormat::UPC_A: return exec0(OneD::UPCAWriter());
74 case BarcodeFormat::UPC_E: return exec0(OneD::UPCEWriter());
75 default: throw std::invalid_argument(std::string("Unsupported format: ") + ToString(_format));
76 }
